.gitignore

Standard ignore rules for:

node_modules

circom build files

snark artifacts

environment variables


REPOSITORY OVERVIEW (Short Version)

Directory	Purpose

/circuits	Zero-knowledge circuits (Circom)
/contracts	All Solidity smart contracts
/interfaces	ABI + frontend integration docs
/frontend/docs	Instructions for calling ADAM from UI
README.md	High-level project summary
README-frontend.md	Frontend integration manual
Whitepaper v6.0	Core research + protocol spec
LICENSE	all rights reserved 
.gitignore	Version control cleanup
